      "text": "🔵 Blue = Authentication\n🟠 Orange = Profile Mgmt\n🟢 Green = AI Chat\n🟣 Purple = Workout Plans\n🟡 Yellow = Security\n──────────────\n(oval) = Use Case\n(stick) = Actor\n─ ─ → «include»\n     required sub-flow\n─ ─ → «extend»\n     optional extension\n→ = Association",
